{"word":"δίωγμα","slug":"δίωγμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δίωγμα</b></el> n (diwg ma_matos neut) <p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:διώκω'><el>διώκω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a pursuit, chase</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>that which is chased, \"the chase, \"</i> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}